          <li><a href="#product-1"><span class="toc-number">1</span>Zenyth Turmeric & Piper Negru, 60 capsule</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-2"><span class="toc-number">2</span>Solaris Turmeric Pudra Bio, 100g</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-3"><span class="toc-number">3</span>Dacia Plant Turmeric Extract, 30 capsule</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-4"><span class="toc-number">4</span>Fares Ceai de Turmeric si Ghimbir, 20 plicuri</a></li>
          <li><a href="#product-5"><span class="toc-number">5</span>ProNatura Curcuma cu Bioperine, 60 capsule</a></li>
          <li><a href="#comparison"><span class="toc-number">6</span>Comparatie rapida: ce supliment cu turmeric si curcuma e pentru tine?</a></li>
          <li><a href="#guide"><span class="toc-number">7</span>Ghid de cumparare: cum alegi cel mai bun turmeric pentru sanatatea ta</a></li>
          <li><a href="#faq"><span class="toc-number">8</span>Intrebari frecvente</a></li>
