        </div>
        <div class="cons">
          <h4>Dezavantaje</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Necesita adaugarea piperului negru separat pentru absorbtie</li>
            <li>Gustul poate fi prea intens pentru unii, necesita dozare atenta</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="product-review" id="product-3">
      <div class="product-header">
        <h2>Dacia Plant Turmeric Extract, 30 capsule</h2>
        <span class="section-tag">~45 lei</span>
      </div>
      
        <div class="specs-grid">
          <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Tip</span><span class="spec-value">supliment alimentar</span></div>
          <div class="spec-item"><span class="spec-label">Cantitate</span><span class="spec-value">30 capsule</span></div>
